  "instructions": [
    "Add chopped cucumber, carrots, daikon, and scallions to a large bowl.",
    "In a small pan, warm soy sauce and rice vinegar over low heat.",
    "Using the binchotan charcoal, create a smoky flavor by placing it near the vegetables or by grilling them for a few seconds.",
    "In a separate pan, toast the sesame seeds until fragrant.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together sesame oil, soy sauce, and rice vinegar.",
    "Add the chilled butter to the vegetable bowl and toss to combine.",
    "Drizzle the sesame oil mixture over the vegetables and toss again.",
    "Sprinkle toasted sesame seeds and chopped cilantro over the top.",
    "Thinly slice the granny smith apple and add it to the bowl.",
    "Toss all the ingredients together and serve chilled, garnished with additional sesame seeds and cilantro if desired."
